---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="The Peel Signal Theory framework: Cycle1924"
  description="Download the Peel Signal Theory framework: how seven signal types turn everyday operational data into clear direction. Written for operators, not statisticians."
  active="whitepaper"
>

<section class="gate">
  <div class="container gate-grid">
    <!-- Copy -->
    <div class="gate-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">Free framework</span>
      <h1>The Peel Signal Theory framework.</h1>
      <p>The thinking behind Cycle1924: how seven signal types turn everyday operational data into clear direction. Written for operators, not statisticians.</p>
      <ul class="gate-points">
        <li><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>The seven signals, explained in plain language</li>
        <li><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>How to find your true operational constraint</li>
        <li><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>A repeatable cycle for measurable results</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="doc-preview">
        <div class="doc-cover">
          <div class="kicker">Cycle1924 · White paper</div>
          <div class="t">The Peel Signal Theory framework</div>
          <div class="lines"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Form -->
    <div>
      <div class="form-card" id="formCard">
        <h2>Download the framework</h2>
        <p class="sub">Enter your details and we'll send the PDF straight to your inbox.</p>
        <form id="wpForm" novalidate>
          <div class="field-row">
            <div class="field">
              <label for="fn">First name</label>
              <input class="input" id="fn" name="firstname" type="text" placeholder="John" required />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label for="ln">Last name</label>
              <input class="input" id="ln" name="lastname" type="text" placeholder="Doe" required />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="co">Company</label>
            <input class="input" id="co" name="company" type="text" placeholder="Acme Inc" required />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="em">Work email</label>
            <input class="input" id="em" name="email" type="email" placeholder="john@example.com" required />
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="ph">Phone <span class="opt">(optional)</span></label>
            <input class="input" id="ph" name="phone" type="tel" placeholder="(555) 123-4567" />
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block" type="submit">Download framework</button>
          <p class="privacy">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
            We respect your privacy. Your info is used to send the framework and follow-up resources.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Success state -->
      <div class="form-card hidden" id="successCard">
        <div class="success">
          <div class="check">
            <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Check your email for the PDF.</h2>
          <p>Thanks, the Peel Signal Theory framework is on its way. If it doesn't arrive in a few minutes, check your spam folder.</p>
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary success-back">Back to home</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<script>
  import { wireHubspotForm } from '../scripts/hubspotForm';
  wireHubspotForm({ formId: 'wpForm', cardId: 'formCard', successId: 'successCard', which: 'whitepaper' });
</script>

<style>
  .gate {
    min-height: calc(100vh - var(--header-h));
    background:
      radial-gradient(900px 480px at 12% 0%, var(--color-accent-soft) 0%, transparent 55%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-white), var(--color-bg-neutral));
    display: flex; align-items: center;
  }
  .gate-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-64); align-items: center;
    padding-block: var(--pad-gate);
  }
  .gate-copy .eyebrow { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: var(--space-18); }
  .gate-copy h1 { font-size: var(--fs-h1-gate); margin-bottom: var(--space-20); }
  .gate-copy p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--fs-108); max-width: 48ch; }
  .gate-points { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: var(--space-28) 0 0; display: grid; gap: var(--space-13); }
  .gate-points li { display: flex; gap: var(--space-12); align-items: flex-start; color: var(--color-text); }
  .gate-points svg { flex: none; color: var(--color-accent); margin-top: 3px; }

  /* Document preview */
  .doc-preview { position: relative; margin-top: var(--space-36); max-width: 380px; }
  .doc-cover {
    background: var(--color-ink-900); color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--r-md); padding: var(--space-28);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transform: rotate(-3deg);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .doc-cover::after { content:""; position:absolute; right:-60px; bottom:-60px; width:180px; height:180px; border-radius:var(--r-circle); background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--color-accent-glow-soft), transparent 65%); }
  .doc-cover .kicker { color:var(--color-accent-light); font-size:var(--fs-072); font-weight:var(--fw-bold); letter-spacing:var(--ls-wide); text-transform:uppercase; }
  .doc-cover .t { font-size:var(--fs-130); font-weight:var(--fw-extrabold); line-height:var(--lh-snug); margin-top:var(--space-10); }
  .doc-cover .lines { margin-top:var(--space-22); display:grid; gap:var(--space-8); }
  .doc-cover .lines span { height:6px; border-radius:var(--r-pill); background: var(--color-overlay-16); }
  .doc-cover .lines span:nth-child(2){ width:80%; } .doc-cover .lines span:nth-child(3){ width:90%; } .doc-cover .lines span:nth-child(4){ width:60%; }

  /* Form card */
  .form-card {
    background: var(--color-white); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--r-xl);
    padding: var(--pad-form-card); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  .form-card h2 { font-size: var(--fs-140); margin-bottom: var(--space-6); }
  .form-card .sub { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--fs-096); margin-bottom: var(--space-26); }
  .privacy { font-size: var(--fs-082); color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-16); line-height: var(--lh-input); display: flex; gap: var(--space-9); align-items: flex-start; }
  .privacy svg { flex: none; margin-top: 2px; color: var(--color-slate-400); }

  /* Success */
  .success { text-align: center; padding: var(--space-14) 0; }
  .success .check {
    width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: var(--r-circle); margin: 0 auto var(--space-20);
    background: var(--color-accent-soft); color: var(--color-accent); display: grid; place-items: center;
  }
  .success h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-10); }
  .success p { color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 38ch; margin-inline: auto; }
  .success-back { margin-top: var(--space-24); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .gate-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-40); }
    .doc-preview { display: none; }
  }
</style>
